#### Razor

####  Project description
Razor a powerful deployment application for bare-metal and virtual servers.

####  Prereqs
GEMS:
mongo(if using mongo)
bson
bson_ext
rspec(if using unit tests)
yaml
syntax


#### Environment variables needed
RAZOR_HOME = root directory for Razor
RAZOR_RSPEC_WEBPATH = local webserver path for writing Rspec HTML output (for unit testing). This is used by './rspec/run_all_unit_tests_html.sh'

#### Directory structure
./bin - control scripts
./conf - configuration YAML files
./images - default images directory
./install - installation bits
./lib - root library folder
./test_scripts - testing scripts
./rspec - unit tests (RSpec)


####  Installation instructions




#### Notes

# Using newest mongo driver build as there is a bug with connect_timeout scoping error that hasn't been merged into available gem yet
# Fix below is assuming RVM
# If using global RVM gems make sure and 'rvm use ruby-1.9.3@global' before installing

wget https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-ruby-driver/zipball/master
unzip master
cd mongodb-mongo-ruby-driver-99d9dfd/
gem build mongo.gemspec
gem install mongo-1.5.2.gem



